# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Merchant — Self-Service Management
#
# CATATAN: Merchant dibuat oleh admin (lihat 06_admin.http).
# Setelah admin buat merchant dan approve, merchant pakai
# api_key dari response POST /admin/merchants untuk request di sini.
#
# Flow:
#   1. Admin: POST /admin/merchants         → dapat api_key & webhook_secret
#   2. Admin: PATCH /admin/merchants/:id/approve
#   3. GET    /v1/merchants/me              → cek profile
#   4. PATCH  /v1/merchants/me             → update profile
#   5. POST   /v1/merchants/me/api-key/regenerate → api_key baru
#   6. POST   /v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts      → tambah rekening
#   7. PATCH  /v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts/:id/primary → set primary
#   8. DELETE /v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts/:id  → hapus rekening
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl       = http://localhost:8080
# Isi dengan api_key dari response POST /admin/merchants
@apiKey        = wpay_test_GANTI_DENGAN_API_KEY_DARI_RESPONSE
# Isi setelah menambah bank account
@bankAccountId = GANTI_DENGAN_ID_BANK_ACCOUNT


### 1. Lihat profile merchant
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 2. Update profile merchant
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "name": "Toko Makmur Jaya Updated",
  "webhook_url": "https://webhook.site/your-unique-id-updated"
}


### 3. Regenerate API key (response: api_key baru — simpan, tidak bisa didapat lagi!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/api-key/regenerate
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 4. Lihat daftar rekening bank
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 5. Tambah rekening bank (isi bankAccountId setelah dapat response)
# Catatan: rekening harus diverifikasi admin sebelum bisa dipakai disbursement
# Max 3 rekening per merchant
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "account_name": "Budi Santoso",
  "set_as_primary": true
}


### 6. Tambah rekening bank kedua
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "bank_code": "BNI",
  "account_number": "9876543210",
  "account_name": "Budi Santoso",
  "set_as_primary": false
}


### 7. Set rekening lain sebagai primary
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts/{{bankAccountId}}/primary
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 8. Hapus rekening bank (tidak bisa hapus primary)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts/{{bankAccountId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 9. Lihat riwayat webhook events
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me/webhook-events
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ERROR CASES ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### API key invalid → 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me
X-API-Key: wpay_test_invalidkeyxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx


### API key tidak dikirim → 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/merchants/me


### Merchant belum di-approve → 403 Forbidden
# (merchant masih status pending)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/payments/va
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_code": "BCA",
  "amount": 10000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "customer_name": "Test",
  "customer_email": "t@t.com",
  "customer_phone": "081200000000",
  "expiry_at": "2027-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}
